text: 4Q or 4q may also refer to: * 4Q, IATA code for Safi Airways * The fourth quarter of a calendar year * The fourth quarter of a fiscal year * A four- quadrant movie, which appeals to all four major demographic quadrants * The 4Q Mangrenade, a 2006 album by Driller Killer * A-4Q, a model of Douglas A-4 Skyhawk * 4Q, designation for one of the Qumran Caves * 4q, an arm of Chromosome 4 (human) *4Q, the production code for the 1977 Doctor Who serial The Face of Evil ==See also== *Q4 (disambiguation)
